data.description: Much sought after neighborhood in South Palm Desert, located in the non-gated community of Canyon Cove community and walking distance to the Haystack tree-lined street.   Pull-in to the custom paver drive with a 2-car garage, one large enough to accommodate higher profile vehicles.  The double door opens to the family room with vaulted ceiling, wood flooring and fireplace.  Sliders open to one of the covered patios, which lead to the backyard that has your own private pool and spa, combination of hardscape and flagstone and another pergola-type patio.   The updated kitchen has tiled flooring, custom tiled backsplash and a dining area that leads to the formal dining area with views of the backyard.  The primary en suite has a walk-in closet with built-in closet organizer, dual sinks, and large, tiled spa-like bathtub with separate shower.  The primary bed has a slider leading to the other covered patio.  The guest bedroom is configured as an en suite, it also has an entrance to the covered patio, plantation shutters and mirrored wardrobe closet.  There is also a guest half bath located in the hallway and a laundry room that leads to a bonus room.  It was used as an office/Movie room and has a built-in desk and many cabinets.  This room could easily be turned into an additional bedroom or add a 3/4 bath and turn it into an additional suite.  The best part is it has its own entrance and could easily be turned into a casita.  Home also includes a solar lease.  This low HOA includes a community swimming pool, spa, tennis courts, and pickleball. El Paseo is close, as well as the Living Desert, hiking and golf!  ALL INFORMATION DEEMED RELIABLE BUT NOT GUARANTEED. AGENT AND BUYERS TO PERFORM DUE DILIGENCE IN RESPECT TO ALL ASPECTS OF THE PROPERTY.  SELLER MAKES NO WARRANTIES EXPRESSED OR IMPLIED AS TO ITS CONDITION.
